<div id="content">
	<h2>簡單4招  Serving Suggestion</h2>
	<p><script type="text/javascript">ddlevelsmenu.setup("1", "topbar","0","0")</script><p><strong><span style="color: #800000;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br /></span></span></span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="web_images/abalone_dish.gif" alt="" width="579" height="454" /><br /></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>第1招</strong>:      打開罐頭將鮑魚與頂湯汁，盛入砂鍋中，無需加蓋，以中火加熱。      &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>第2招</strong>:      待頂湯加熱至微微沸騰並升起縷縷白煙，迅速將鮑魚夾出並盛入盤中。      &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>第3招</strong>:      鍋中頂湯繼續加熱至完全沸騰後，即可熄火。&nbsp;</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: comic sans ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>第4招</strong>:      然後將頂湯汁加熱往均勻澆淋於鮑魚上, 熱騰騰的阿一鮑魚即可上桌。</span></span></li>
</ul></p>
</div>
